1035
00:54:17,254 --> 00:54:22,191
I've just guaranteed the bank sufficient funds to meet their needs.

1036
00:54:22,559 --> 00:54:25,892
They'll close up for a week and then reopen.

1037
00:54:26,796 --> 00:54:28,559
