1056
00:55:38,935 --> 00:55:41,927
Well, no, Charlie. I didn't even ask him. We don't need Potter over here.

1057
00:55:42,038 --> 00:55:43,699
Then, I'll take mine now.

1058
00:55:44,174 --> 00:55:45,732
No, but you're...

1059
