1111
00:57:44,627 --> 00:57:46,288
How much do you need?

1112
00:57:46,396 --> 00:57:49,832
Hey! I got $2,000.

1113
00:57:50,500 --> 00:57:52,968
Here's $2,000. This'll tide us over till the bank reopens.

1114
00:57:53,069 --> 00:57:55,833
- All right, Tom, how much do you need? - $242.

1115
00:57:55,939 --> 00:57:58,430
Tom, just enough to tide you over until the bank reopens.

1116
00:57:58,541 --> 00:58:00,702
I'll take $242.

1117
00:58:03,513 --> 00:58:05,276
- There you are. - That'll close my account.

