1133
00:58:43,453 --> 00:58:47,913
...five, four, three, two,

1134
00:58:48,091 --> 00:58:50,150
one, bingo!

1135
00:58:50,260 --> 00:58:51,887
We made it! Close the door, Eustace! We made it.

1136
00:58:51,995 --> 00:58:54,896
Look, look, we're still in business. We've still got 2 bucks left.

1137
00:58:54,998 --> 00:58:56,795
Look, let's have some of that. Let's celebrate!

1138
00:58:56,900 --> 00:58:58,299
