1194
01:04:14,981 --> 01:04:17,848
All right, kids, here. Here, get in here.

1195
01:04:17,984 --> 01:04:20,111
Now, one at a time. Get right up on the seat there.

1196
01:04:21,688 --> 01:04:25,317
